  "title": "Backend Developer",
  "description": "<ul><li>Assist the Lead on agile development and delivery of solutions.</li><li>Function within a team of like-minded engineers to ensure that the platform are operating optimally in terms of availability, capacity, security & business continuity.</li><li>Plan, manage, implement project and operation to Government technology standards and policy.</li><li>Review and recommend relevant industry best practices for Government IT infrastructure/SMP for adoption.</li></ul><p><strong>Primary Wanted traits:</strong></p><ul><li>Strong javascript Developer with actual hands on experience</li><li>Motivated individual willing to learn new technologies</li><li>Working experience with ServiceNow / equivalent platforms</li></ul><p><strong>Desirable traits:</strong></p><p><strong>Technical Skills</strong></p><ul><li>Javascript (Node JS, ReactJS typescript, Generic javascript)</li><li>CSS</li><li>Angular JS</li><li>AWS experience (EKS, serverless)</li><li>Understands and able to troubleshoot basic network and systems issues</li><li>Full Stack developer</li></ul><p><strong>Good to have:</strong></p><ul><li>Able to communicate well</li><li>Ability to manage and follow through projects</li><li>Technical Skills</li><li>Python</li><li>Bash scripting</li><li>Powershell scripting</li><li>ITIL</li></ul>",
